NAFO Divisions (Bounded)

Source: R/data_NAFO_Divsions_2021_line_enclosed.R
NAFO_Divisions_2021_line_enclosed.Rd

An sf object that depicts the boundaries of the NAFO regions

data("NAFO_Divisions_2021_line_enclosed")

Format

An sf object:

Geometry type

LINESTRING

Dimension

XY

Bounding box

xmin: -80 ymin: 35 xmax: -42 ymax: 78.16667

Geodetic CRS

NAD83

Features

38 x 5

Metadata

See source

Source
